headline: GE: Q4 Earnings Snapshot
summary: EVENDALE, Ohio (AP) — GE Aerospace (GE) on Thursday reported fourth-quarter earnings of $2.54 billion. The Evendale, Ohio-based company said it had profit of $2.40 per share. Earnings, adjusted for non-recurring gains and to account for discontinued operations, came to $1.57 per share.

content.title: GE: Q4 Earnings Snapshot
content.summary: EVENDALE, Ohio (AP) — GE Aerospace (GE) on Thursday reported fourth-quarter earnings of $2.54 billion. The Evendale, Ohio-based company said it had profit of $2.40 per share. Earnings, adjusted for non-recurring gains and to account for discontinued operations, came to $1.57 per share.
